WEBVTT

00:00:00.080 --> 00:00:35.240
Subtitle Provide by dramacool.asia Translator [Admin.@YNG]

00:01:09.760 --> 00:01:10.600
Zhang Ji

00:01:10.600 --> 00:01:11.080
You

00:01:11.080 --> 00:01:12.120
Why are you here?

00:01:12.720 --> 00:01:13.240
This...

00:01:13.240 --> 00:01:14.280
Where is this?

00:01:14.800 --> 00:01:16.080
Young Master Li, don't be nervous.

00:01:16.440 --> 00:01:17.720
I came here this time

00:01:17.720 --> 00:01:19.720
to apologize to you.

00:01:20.080 --> 00:01:21.200
Apologize?

00:01:21.200 --> 00:01:22.680
Apologize for what?

00:01:23.240 --> 00:01:25.560
Last time you came to my pearl trading house to collect a debt,

00:01:25.840 --> 00:01:27.040
but left empty-handed.

00:01:27.040 --> 00:01:28.920
I truly had no choice.

00:01:29.520 --> 00:01:30.480
However,

00:01:30.880 --> 00:01:32.520
when it comes to official matters,

00:01:33.160 --> 00:01:35.120
I must handle them properly.

00:01:35.400 --> 00:01:36.280
Don't come any closer.

00:01:36.520 --> 00:01:37.440
Keep your distance.

00:01:37.600 --> 00:01:38.800
Just say what you need to say.

00:01:39.480 --> 00:01:41.960
I feel I owe you.

00:01:41.960 --> 00:01:43.440
This southern pearl trading house

00:01:43.440 --> 00:01:45.560
is also responsible for the livelihood of Hepu's people.

00:01:45.960 --> 00:01:48.160
I admit my abilities are limited.

00:01:48.840 --> 00:01:50.440
It's hard for me to bear such a heavy responsibility.

00:01:50.600 --> 00:01:51.520
So,

00:01:51.840 --> 00:01:54.400
I wish to ask you to take charge of the southern pearl trading house.

00:01:55.440 --> 00:01:56.640
I...

00:01:57.040 --> 00:01:58.800
The manager of the southern pearl trading house?

00:01:59.160 --> 00:02:00.840
Couldn't you have asked me about this during the day?

00:02:00.840 --> 00:02:02.080
Why did you bring me here?

00:02:02.720 --> 00:02:04.360
Young Master Li, you are

00:02:04.360 --> 00:02:06.480
the head of the top pearl family in the south.

00:02:06.480 --> 00:02:08.680
Now you also lead in Hepu's pearl trading houses.

00:02:08.680 --> 00:02:09.760
You hold the top position.

00:02:09.760 --> 00:02:11.520
In all of Hepu,

00:02:12.240 --> 00:02:15.040
no one is more suitable than you.

00:02:15.360 --> 00:02:16.480
So,

00:02:16.480 --> 00:02:18.320
my father wishes to show his sincerity.

00:02:19.360 --> 00:02:21.160
He asked me to serve you in this way.

00:02:21.160 --> 00:02:22.680
to be by your side.

00:02:24.240 --> 00:02:25.120
The Prefect

00:02:25.120 --> 00:02:26.400
is truly willing to invest.

00:02:26.880 --> 00:02:28.600
I believe

00:02:29.640 --> 00:02:31.280
I have some worth myself.

00:02:45.840 --> 00:02:47.680
On such a beautiful night,

00:02:49.320 --> 00:02:51.640
why not show me some kindness?

00:03:15.040 --> 00:03:16.120
It hurts, Young Master.

00:03:19.000 --> 00:03:19.400
Please be gentle.

00:03:19.400 --> 00:03:20.080
It hurts.

00:03:20.480 --> 00:03:22.200
What do you think you are?

00:03:22.520 --> 00:03:23.640
Don't think I don't know.

00:03:24.160 --> 00:03:25.560
Every move you make now

00:03:25.560 --> 00:03:27.360
disgusts me.

00:03:28.480 --> 00:03:30.360
I don't know

00:03:30.680 --> 00:03:32.400
what I've done to offend you.

00:03:32.840 --> 00:03:34.520
to make you hate me so much.

00:03:34.880 --> 00:03:37.200
I only wish to stay by your side

00:03:37.840 --> 00:03:39.200
and serve you.

00:03:54.040 --> 00:03:55.040
Miss Zhang,

00:03:55.960 --> 00:03:57.440
just speak your mind.

00:04:03.560 --> 00:04:05.240
Here in Hepu,

00:04:05.720 --> 00:04:07.680
nothing is greater than official power.

00:04:08.600 --> 00:04:10.120
Wang Cheng was foolish.

00:04:10.120 --> 00:04:11.920
His death is no loss.

00:04:12.880 --> 00:04:13.960
Actually, my father

00:04:13.960 --> 00:04:16.520
truly wants to work with you, Young Master.

00:04:16.520 --> 00:04:19.600
If you join my father's side,

00:04:20.240 --> 00:04:22.160
in the future here in Hepu,

00:04:22.160 --> 00:04:24.600
anything you wish to do

00:04:25.200 --> 00:04:27.560
will go smoothly.

00:04:28.120 --> 00:04:29.360
That's it.

00:04:31.080 --> 00:04:32.040
Of course,

00:04:32.160 --> 00:04:34.880
any trouble you face

00:04:35.080 --> 00:04:36.840
my Prefect's office

00:04:37.040 --> 00:04:39.000
can help you resolve them all.

00:04:39.480 --> 00:04:41.040
Besides,

00:04:41.040 --> 00:04:42.840
I am sincere

00:04:42.840 --> 00:04:44.920
in offering myself to you.

00:04:46.760 --> 00:04:48.640
We both know what the Prefect wants.

00:04:48.960 --> 00:04:50.720
You and I understand.

00:04:51.240 --> 00:04:52.840
If you want to take on me, Li Ling,

00:04:53.280 --> 00:04:54.320
let's see

00:04:54.320 --> 00:04:56.160
if you have the bite for it.

00:05:00.240 --> 00:05:01.400
Li Ling,

00:05:01.760 --> 00:05:03.320
you're dead set

00:05:03.320 --> 00:05:05.120
on opposing my Prefect's office, aren't you?

00:05:06.720 --> 00:05:07.680
I, Li Ling,

00:05:07.880 --> 00:05:09.520
am just a commoner.

00:05:09.520 --> 00:05:11.000
Though poor,

00:05:11.280 --> 00:05:12.600
my backbone

00:05:12.600 --> 00:05:14.080
is strong.

00:05:14.720 --> 00:05:15.360
Fine.

00:05:15.960 --> 00:05:17.840
Then I hope, Young Master,

00:05:18.080 --> 00:05:20.520
you won't regret this.

00:05:21.560 --> 00:05:23.520
Let me give you some advice, Miss.

00:05:24.000 --> 00:05:25.440
As a woman,

00:05:25.520 --> 00:05:27.880
if you lack even basic decency,

00:05:28.080 --> 00:05:30.600
and only think of using your body to rise,

00:05:31.000 --> 00:05:32.600
even if you reach the top,

00:05:33.040 --> 00:05:33.960
one day,

00:05:34.120 --> 00:05:36.560
you'll be discarded like trash.

00:05:45.840 --> 00:05:47.720
Hurry and speak!

00:05:48.000 --> 00:05:49.520
I've searched all over Hepu.

00:05:49.520 --> 00:05:50.720
I can't find Young Master anywhere.

00:05:50.720 --> 00:05:52.600
All I know is, after he left home that day,

00:05:52.600 --> 00:05:54.360
he disappeared.

00:05:56.680 --> 00:05:57.400
What should we do?

00:05:57.800 --> 00:05:58.600
What now?

00:05:58.880 --> 00:06:00.640
Li Ling must not get into trouble!

00:06:02.440 --> 00:06:04.040
Li Ling,

00:06:04.040 --> 00:06:06.880
someone raised in luxury like you,

00:06:06.880 --> 00:06:09.240
who knows nothing of hardship,

00:06:09.560 --> 00:06:11.080
can never understand

00:06:11.080 --> 00:06:12.600
the struggles of people like me.

00:06:13.160 --> 00:06:14.240
But

00:06:14.240 --> 00:06:16.160
you should think carefully

00:06:16.160 --> 00:06:17.800
about how you'll get out of this.

00:06:19.000 --> 00:06:20.920
Unaware of suffering—

00:06:21.880 --> 00:06:23.800
how ironic.

00:06:28.360 --> 00:06:28.960
I...

00:06:29.240 --> 00:06:29.800
I...

00:06:30.160 --> 00:06:31.280
Where are my clothes?

00:06:31.440 --> 00:06:32.200
Zhang Ji!

00:06:32.200 --> 00:06:33.600
Give me back my clothes!

00:06:33.800 --> 00:06:34.400
You—

00:06:34.640 --> 00:06:36.200
You're shameless!

00:06:36.640 --> 00:06:37.400
Useless.

00:06:37.960 --> 00:06:38.960
Useless.

00:06:39.280 --> 00:06:40.840
A spoiled rich heir

00:06:40.840 --> 00:06:41.920
and you can't even handle him.

00:06:42.600 --> 00:06:44.160
What's the point of keeping you?

00:06:45.080 --> 00:06:46.080
Truly,

00:06:46.080 --> 00:06:48.320
a lowborn child.

00:06:48.320 --> 00:06:49.520
If not for your brother

00:06:49.520 --> 00:06:51.200
being held hostage in the capital,

00:06:51.320 --> 00:06:53.040
I wouldn't spare you.

00:06:55.360 --> 00:06:56.640
So useless,

00:06:57.320 --> 00:06:59.040
yet you want your mother's memorial tablet

00:06:59.040 --> 00:07:00.600
placed in my Zhang family's ancestral hall?

00:07:00.800 --> 00:07:01.760
Keep dreaming.

00:07:05.960 --> 00:07:06.600
Father,

00:07:06.600 --> 00:07:08.080
I know I was wrong.

00:07:10.280 --> 00:07:11.920
But I have another way.

00:07:11.920 --> 00:07:13.880
I can still fix everything.

00:07:16.280 --> 00:07:17.520
Since

00:07:18.040 --> 00:07:19.880
he wants to go all the way down this path,

00:07:22.400 --> 00:07:25.240
let's make sure he doesn't see tomorrow's sun.

00:07:33.840 --> 00:07:34.680
Young Master

00:07:36.560 --> 00:07:38.160
Why are you up so late?

00:07:38.960 --> 00:07:39.840
Shh, quiet.

00:07:39.840 --> 00:07:40.960
Let me tell you.

00:07:40.960 --> 00:07:42.200
Where did you go?

00:07:42.200 --> 00:07:43.560
Just now, a foreign lady

00:07:43.560 --> 00:07:44.360
came by with money.

00:07:44.480 --> 00:07:45.440
She even took your clothes.

00:07:45.440 --> 00:07:47.520
I knew you'd tell him.

00:07:50.160 --> 00:07:51.560
The money's already delivered.

00:07:51.560 --> 00:07:52.360
That was fast.

00:07:56.880 --> 00:07:57.720
Our Li family

00:07:57.720 --> 00:07:59.120
may not have money now,

00:07:59.560 --> 00:08:01.240
but we're not so desperate

00:08:01.240 --> 00:08:03.600
that you'd need to make such sacrifices.

00:08:03.720 --> 00:08:04.440
Ah.

00:08:04.800 --> 00:08:05.720
Hey.

00:08:06.080 --> 00:08:07.040
This humble woman

00:08:07.040 --> 00:08:09.440
may have come from humble origins,

00:08:09.440 --> 00:08:10.680
but I've never

00:08:11.280 --> 00:08:11.800
Hey.

00:08:11.800 --> 00:08:12.480
What do you mean?

00:08:12.480 --> 00:08:13.640
Explain yourselves.

00:08:14.680 --> 00:08:15.760
You said before

00:08:16.000 --> 00:08:17.560
you'd handle other matters.

00:08:17.960 --> 00:08:19.640
I know you pity our hardships,

00:08:19.800 --> 00:08:20.840
but you shouldn't have

00:08:20.840 --> 00:08:21.960
made such a deal

00:08:22.160 --> 00:08:23.080
with that foreign woman.

00:08:25.760 --> 00:08:26.920
However,

00:08:27.360 --> 00:08:28.920
compared to your status,

00:08:28.920 --> 00:08:30.280
I am nothing.

00:08:30.680 --> 00:08:32.560
I truly feel ashamed.

00:08:39.040 --> 00:08:39.640
I...

00:08:39.880 --> 00:08:40.760
Young Master,

00:08:40.760 --> 00:08:42.160
I could do it too.

00:08:42.160 --> 00:08:43.480
I'm healthy.

00:08:46.600 --> 00:08:47.920
I can do it.

00:08:50.320 --> 00:08:51.160
I...

00:08:51.400 --> 00:08:52.880
I can't be bothered to explain.

00:08:52.880 --> 00:08:53.360
Honestly...

00:08:53.360 --> 00:08:54.560
I'm really speechless.

00:09:01.640 --> 00:09:02.800
Oh?

00:09:03.920 --> 00:09:05.200
Sir Li,

00:09:05.200 --> 00:09:06.680
you're in quite the mood.

00:09:07.400 --> 00:09:08.800
You killed someone,

00:09:08.800 --> 00:09:09.840
yet still enjoy yourself.

00:09:09.840 --> 00:09:11.320
Enjoying comfort here.

00:09:13.640 --> 00:09:14.840
Men...

00:09:15.160 --> 00:09:16.840
It's just Chief Constable Sun.

00:09:16.840 --> 00:09:18.040
In the middle of the night,

00:09:18.040 --> 00:09:19.040
making such a scene,

00:09:19.040 --> 00:09:20.240
breaking into a home.

00:09:20.480 --> 00:09:22.160
Now you say I killed someone.

00:09:22.160 --> 00:09:23.400
Who did I kill?

00:09:24.000 --> 00:09:26.200
Still denying it at death's door.

00:09:26.440 --> 00:09:28.960
I can't stand you crooked merchants.

00:09:29.200 --> 00:09:30.120
You suck people's blood,

00:09:30.720 --> 00:09:33.720
and act all righteous.

00:09:35.280 --> 00:09:36.120
Hand him over!

00:09:36.120 --> 00:09:36.920
Arrest him!

00:09:37.160 --> 00:09:38.160
Wait!

00:09:38.840 --> 00:09:39.920
May I ask, Chief Constable Sun,

00:09:40.520 --> 00:09:42.080
what crime has Li Ling committed

00:09:42.360 --> 00:09:44.320
to warrant such a show of force?

00:09:44.480 --> 00:09:45.800
The criminal Li Ling

00:09:46.560 --> 00:09:49.320
murdered Wang Cheng, manager of Wang's pearl trading house.

00:09:49.720 --> 00:09:50.960
The evidence is solid.

00:09:51.360 --> 00:09:52.760
By order of the Prefect,

00:09:52.920 --> 00:09:54.120
he is to be arrested.

00:09:54.480 --> 00:09:55.800
You're lying!

00:09:56.040 --> 00:09:57.360
Wang Cheng hanged himself.

00:09:57.360 --> 00:09:58.240
Everyone knows that.

00:09:58.600 --> 00:10:00.120
The coroner examined him.

00:10:00.400 --> 00:10:03.040
Wang Cheng was murdered.

00:10:03.040 --> 00:10:04.600
It was staged as a suicide.

00:10:04.600 --> 00:10:06.440
What does that have to do with Li Ling?

00:10:06.840 --> 00:10:08.800
That's not for me to know.

00:10:09.280 --> 00:10:10.760
I'm just following orders.

00:10:10.760 --> 00:10:12.080
If anyone interferes,

00:10:12.480 --> 00:10:13.520
they'll be arrested too.

00:10:13.520 --> 00:10:14.000
Hey!

00:10:14.240 --> 00:10:15.160
Chief Constable Sun,

00:10:15.360 --> 00:10:16.200
I'll go with you.

00:10:17.360 --> 00:10:18.760
Don't trouble anyone else.

00:10:20.920 --> 00:10:22.600
At least you know how to behave.

00:10:24.360 --> 00:10:25.440
Take him away.

00:10:26.240 --> 00:10:27.560
Wait!

00:10:28.160 --> 00:10:29.120
Don't worry about me.

00:10:29.120 --> 00:10:30.320
Go find Kana.

00:10:30.520 --> 00:10:31.400
Tell her

00:10:31.400 --> 00:10:32.600
the thing she promised me

00:10:32.600 --> 00:10:33.400
needs to be done.

00:10:38.200 --> 00:10:38.640
Li Ling!

00:10:38.640 --> 00:10:39.520
Sister!

00:10:40.640 --> 00:10:41.160
Don't be rash.

00:10:41.160 --> 00:10:42.640
Do as Sir Li said.

00:10:52.640 --> 00:10:53.680
Will you confess or not?

00:10:54.080 --> 00:10:55.120
Are you going to confess?

00:10:56.760 --> 00:10:58.520
You're quite stubborn.

00:10:58.760 --> 00:11:00.200
No one's ever

00:11:00.200 --> 00:11:01.240
made it through a night with me.

00:11:01.240 --> 00:11:02.640
Prefect Zhang has arrived.

00:11:04.360 --> 00:11:05.400
Chief Constable Sun.

00:11:05.520 --> 00:11:06.840
You can't keep beating him.

00:11:06.840 --> 00:11:08.760
I've given you all my pearls.

00:11:08.760 --> 00:11:10.400
There's nothing left even if you keep hitting me.

00:11:10.400 --> 00:11:11.800
Chief Constable Sun.

00:11:13.680 --> 00:11:14.600
Prefect Zhang.

00:11:14.600 --> 00:11:15.240
Prefect Zhang.

00:11:15.320 --> 00:11:15.800
Prefect Zhang.

00:11:16.040 --> 00:11:18.080
I've given all my pearls to Chief Constable Sun.

00:11:18.080 --> 00:11:19.000
I have nothing left.

00:11:19.000 --> 00:11:19.800
I really have nothing left.

00:11:19.800 --> 00:11:21.600
Prefect Zhang, don't listen to his nonsense.

00:11:22.000 --> 00:11:22.880
I wouldn't dare.

00:11:22.880 --> 00:11:24.000
I don't have any.

00:11:24.200 --> 00:11:25.480
You wouldn't dare?

00:11:25.480 --> 00:11:26.600
You still wouldn't dare?

00:11:26.760 --> 00:11:28.240
All my pearls are with him.

00:11:28.360 --> 00:11:29.760
If you don't believe me, search him.

00:11:29.760 --> 00:11:30.800
So many pearls.

00:11:30.800 --> 00:11:32.640
And many are rare pearls of unmatched quality.

00:11:32.640 --> 00:11:33.400
Prefect Zhang.

00:11:34.400 --> 00:11:35.160
Prefect Zhang.

00:11:35.280 --> 00:11:36.160
I wouldn't dare.

00:11:36.280 --> 00:11:36.920
Prefect Zhang.

00:11:37.680 --> 00:11:38.800
They're all here, Prefect Zhang.

00:11:38.800 --> 00:11:40.200
I've given them all to you, Prefect Zhang.

00:11:40.520 --> 00:11:41.400
I wouldn't dare.

00:11:41.400 --> 00:11:42.040
Prefect Zhang.

00:11:42.040 --> 00:11:43.560
Please spare me, Prefect Zhang.

00:11:44.320 --> 00:11:45.200
Prefect Zhang.

00:11:46.720 --> 00:11:47.960
Chief Constable Sun.

00:11:48.400 --> 00:11:50.080
You have some nerve.

00:11:50.080 --> 00:11:52.480
You dare steal right in front of me?

00:11:53.680 --> 00:11:55.920
Look how fat you've gotten.

00:11:56.120 --> 00:11:57.640
You must have taken plenty.

00:11:57.880 --> 00:11:59.360
And you call yourself a constable.

00:11:59.640 --> 00:12:01.480
You probably can't even catch a frog now.

00:12:01.680 --> 00:12:02.440
Take him away.

00:12:02.440 --> 00:12:03.840
Give him twenty heavy blows.

00:12:04.120 --> 00:12:06.120
Spare me, Prefect Zhang!

00:12:06.840 --> 00:12:08.560
You're framing me!

00:12:12.400 --> 00:12:13.880
Young Master Li.

00:12:13.880 --> 00:12:15.120
Handled like this,

00:12:15.120 --> 00:12:16.680
are you satisfied?

00:12:17.000 --> 00:12:17.840
Prefect Zhang.

00:12:18.160 --> 00:12:19.520
I'm innocent!

00:12:19.680 --> 00:12:21.800
Please clear my name, Prefect Zhang!

00:12:24.200 --> 00:12:25.200
Young Master Li.

00:12:25.880 --> 00:12:27.000
It seems

00:12:27.720 --> 00:12:29.640
you still don't know why you're here.

00:12:29.640 --> 00:12:31.200
You still don't understand, do you?

00:12:34.120 --> 00:12:35.040
I don't know.

00:12:35.040 --> 00:12:37.240
I just made a deal with the sea traders.

00:12:37.400 --> 00:12:39.760
I came back and you arrested me, Prefect Zhang.

00:12:40.000 --> 00:12:40.400
I...

00:12:40.400 --> 00:12:41.760
I don't know anything.

00:12:42.000 --> 00:12:43.520
And that Shopkeeper Wang,

00:12:43.680 --> 00:12:44.520
his death

00:12:44.520 --> 00:12:46.520
has nothing to do with me.

00:12:46.520 --> 00:12:47.840
Prefect Zhang.

00:12:48.000 --> 00:12:49.040
Ah...

00:12:49.120 --> 00:12:50.480
You're about to die,

00:12:50.480 --> 00:12:53.160
and you're still spouting nonsense.

00:12:54.080 --> 00:12:54.800
Prefect Zhang.

00:12:54.800 --> 00:12:55.600
Wait a moment.

00:12:56.680 --> 00:12:57.760
What did you just say?

00:12:59.600 --> 00:13:01.840
You did business with the sea traders?

00:13:02.920 --> 00:13:03.840
Yes, yes.

00:13:04.400 --> 00:13:05.520
What kind of business?

00:13:06.640 --> 00:13:08.080
P-pearls.

00:13:08.520 --> 00:13:10.120
I sold all my pearls

00:13:10.120 --> 00:13:11.640
to them.

00:13:17.080 --> 00:13:18.160
Serve me well.

00:13:18.800 --> 00:13:20.240
Prefect Zhang.

00:13:20.520 --> 00:13:21.960
Prefect Zhang.